Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织田真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.67,0:00:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会忘记带练习日志呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉良君的状况好像不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙认真的有点超过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田！\N武田君你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.63,0:01:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.03,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想留更多时间给练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.25,0:01:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿这样你才会受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.65,0:01:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样你才会受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.12,0:01:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就地这样你才会受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.65,0:01:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.59,0:01:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.72,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你回家冰敷吧\N你们两个在搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续给我跑起来\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.14,0:01:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿包包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.47,0:02:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田君 还好吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚跟他有聊仕么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.98,0:02:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.72,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.99,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（想要丈夫学生的肉棒）\N（口交中毒的人妻）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 脚还痛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.68,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不痛一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N还痛就要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要稍微出点力喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无论如何\N都想赢得下一次的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.26,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上最近跟女朋友交分手了\N有点心烦意乱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有点激进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要减少摄取水分\N来减轻自己的体重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到男孩子也会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一些傻事\N来分散自己失恋的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦\N师母你就不要笑我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的感觉真的很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 翻过来躺正吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我继续咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果会痛要跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 年轻嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面都这么有元气\N应该好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 按摩结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师母谢谢祢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师母 你真的好性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以刚刚才会不小心硬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到我这样的\N还这么有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 非常有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田君你真爱说笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脚会扭伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是因为水分不足\N营养也跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子会饿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我早餐还没有吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我去帮你准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道可不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再帮我按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是今天也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你要说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 那么\N我先准备煮饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 喝吧\N嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田君他去年拿了亚军\N所以他今年无论如何都想赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想帮助他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田他有个比他大两岁的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他哥哥也是田径队的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是拿到亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.77,0:08:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是想连哥哥的份一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田也带着我的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.32,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟好不容易有这么好的队员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.79,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我也知道拿到\N第一并不是全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看着他每天这样练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.67,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会尽我的一份力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我的很不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很想你给他们按摩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子 你是我的老婆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以给他们按摩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这跟你刚刚说的又不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很久没做了\N而且今天我状态不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天那个来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们下次再做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.98,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次教你的按摩方法\N你有试试吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.52,0:10:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次做的那个\N可以再麻烦你一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个动作我在家可能比较无法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（来老师家里可以看到好玩的事情）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟小司\N做了色色的事情对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小司他给了真子老师情书的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.28,0:13:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来队员们都知道了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.08,0:13:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都觉得你真的人很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.29,0:13:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是\N因为你是我们老师的老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们也不能想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们会怀疑\N我跟小司做过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小司自己跟我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他跟你做色色的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是小司亲口说的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会说谎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也喜欢真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N到底怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 冷静一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冷静不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是小司说谎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一想到你跟小司做过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.35,0:14:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要在乱想了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 跟我做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.22,0:14:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说爽吗\N我就真的没跟小司做过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连情书都没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我求你\N不要在这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在真子\N老师的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我就会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.31,0:14:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 跟我做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再让我困扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 你看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 你看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我的大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我求你了\N冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我这样叫我怎么冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次这么真心的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬成这种程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快硬死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法参加社团活动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你刚才说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟本没办法集中精神练习了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.43,0:15:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我拜托你了\N不要离开田径队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师\N请跟我做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老公可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你的老师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以做这种事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是退出田径队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样\N你就不算我的师母了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要退出田径队\N好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是要退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你的心意我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结了婚后就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有被这样称赞过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做爱是真的不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是做爱以外的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N那就用手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 还是用嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我口交吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口交吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我舔咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.11,0:22:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.78,0:22:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舔咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.72,0:23:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.71,0:24:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.19,0:24:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.00,0:25:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 我好舒服\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.01,0:25:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我嘴里面射出来吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.61,0:25:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗\N我也快射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.57,0:25:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 我快射了\N没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.68,0:26:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 我要射了\N可以射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.29,0:26:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.46,0:27:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.73,0:27:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.39,0:27:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以告诉任何人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.46,0:27:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.47,0:27:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要退出田径队了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:28.14,0:27:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.21,0:27:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.41,0:27:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我帮你清干净吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.25,0:28:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么感觉你有点不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.12,0:28:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都那么久没做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.13,0:28:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已经很多个月都没做了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.53,0:28:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.53,0:28:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.33,0:28:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.29,0:28:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.90,0:29:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么这么紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.77,0:29:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很久没做了\N啊 好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.77,0:29:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊\N慢慢来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.97,0:29:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.78,0:29:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.58,0:29:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.45,0:29:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了\N进去一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.39,0:29:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.02,0:30:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.42,0:30:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.43,0:30:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.43,0:30:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.43,0:30:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.43,0:30:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.43,0:30:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N先冷静一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:16.04,0:30:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.97,0:30:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.11,0:30:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.92,0:30:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们就睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.85,0:30:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧 下次在给你\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.65,0:30:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样吧\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.84,0:31:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天10点才会回来\N晚餐就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.37,0:31:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.91,0:31:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全喔\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.91,0:31:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.91,0:31:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田君他最近怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.52,0:31:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.52,0:31:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的状况非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.86,0:31:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是托你的福吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.59,0:31:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他体力变好了\N体能也在最佳状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.93,0:31:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这次能拿第一名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.13,0:31:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.34,0:31:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.07,0:31:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.21,0:31:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.21,0:32:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.75,0:32:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天回来我们来做吧\N嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.25,0:32:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在那之后就没在见过他了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.39,0:32:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（对他的想念在逐步上升）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.99,0:32:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（也许）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.46,0:32:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我想也许是我的身体在想他）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.47,0:32:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（一直在想着那一天的“按摩”）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.40,0:33:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（没错）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.60,0:33:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我的确是对那个）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.01,0:33:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那个又硬 而且又持久）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.28,0:33:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（被那根大肉棒所吸引）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.61,0:33:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那是一种前所未有的感觉）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.82,0:33:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（看着那根大肉棒想着一边舔着）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.16,0:33:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（要是在见到那根大肉棒的话）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.16,0:33:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（正当我这么想时）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.70,0:33:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（小司君就出现了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.57,0:33:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（叮咚）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.11,0:33:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.59,0:33:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（叮咚）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.06,0:33:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.94,0:34:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.47,0:34:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.81,0:34:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚好像怪怪的\N可以麻烦你帮我着看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.21,0:34:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有健二邢问问说\N正确的按摩方法之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:21.22,0:34:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也有扭到的地方\N所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.29,0:34:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 进来里面坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.36,0:34:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.51,0:34:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.19,0:34:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.67,0:35:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.40,0:35:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.87,0:35:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.54,0:35:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.55,0:35:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.82,0:35:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.48,0:35:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.55,0:35:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.56,0:35:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.82,0:35:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.76,0:35:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.36,0:35:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.56,0:35:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.90,0:35:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.37,0:35:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.31,0:35:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.92,0:36:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.12,0:36:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.52,0:36:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.99,0:36:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.99,0:36:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看他拉筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.00,0:36:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.00,0:36:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.00,0:36:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.81,0:36:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.81,0:36:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是跟武田做色色的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.15,0:36:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.35,0:36:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟我解释\N这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.09,0:36:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健二君在这里\N我不太好说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.83,0:36:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:52.30,0:36:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好跟你解释的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.30,0:36:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.38,0:37:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N我来教你正确的拉筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.85,0:37:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是寝室吗\N不行 你不进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.53,0:37:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.20,0:37:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里跟武田做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.80,0:37:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才没有做是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.27,0:37:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他什么都没有发生\N我发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.15,0:37:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢武田吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.42,0:37:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有喜欢上他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.02,0:37:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看到他很烦恼的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.76,0:37:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪吗\N只是看到他很烦恼的样子就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.23,0:37:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一从开始就喜欢你的我却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.17,0:38:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连情书都不读
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.77,0:38:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是我怎么样都和和没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.24,0:38:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.84,0:38:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有想到小司你你的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.05,0:38:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我是有丈夫的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.45,0:38:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.52,0:38:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是\N我丈夫的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.66,0:38:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样没错\N但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.06,0:38:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我\N你什么都不会为我做的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.93,0:38:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么喜欢你的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.27,0:38:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连真子老师你都拒绝我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.07,0:38:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.47,0:38:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去怎么办\N连跑步也会跑不动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.82,0:38:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.89,0:39:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常在想\N我可以做些什么来帮助你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.83,0:39:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我终于想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.90,0:39:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让田径队的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.50,0:39:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都可以精精神奕奕的练习\N我要用我的方法来帮助大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.38,0:39:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.32,0:39:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把衣服脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.65,0:39:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.99,0:39:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.42,0:39:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.42,0:40:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都硬成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.59,0:40:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.80,0:40:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.80,0:40:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.29,0:41:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.83,0:41:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是一直想让我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.50,0:41:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我含着你这根大肉棒的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.97,0:41:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.97,0:41:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.78,0:41:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师\N我 这是我的第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.65,0:41:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.92,0:41:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会一直喜欢着小司的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.93,0:41:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.59,0:41:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.74,0:42:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.82,0:42:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.49,0:42:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.42,0:42:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么可不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.56,0:42:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以\N舔的让你更舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.50,0:42:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.32,0:42:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.13,0:42:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.95,0:43:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师\N你舔肉棒的样子真淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.51,0:43:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.24,0:43:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.38,0:43:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.71,0:43:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽到不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.18,0:43:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.65,0:43:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.46,0:43:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我告诉你什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.46,0:43:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个地方让你最爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.66,0:44:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.73,0:44:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.40,0:44:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在床上躺好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.40,0:44:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.74,0:44:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.75,0:44:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你更爽\N忍耐一下先不要射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:22.48,0:44:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那里\N好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.89,0:44:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.23,0:44:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这边好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.26,0:45:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.73,0:45:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.23,0:45:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看你的屁眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.90,0:45:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.04,0:45:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连这边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.79,0:46:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看到自己的大肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.42,0:46:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肉棒真的好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:41.96,0:46:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师的嘴\N太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.03,0:46:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.98,0:47:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.98,0:47:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒还是这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.15,0:47:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是想摸我的大奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:50.69,0:47:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:01.50,0:48:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起变舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.77,0:48:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.51,0:48:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要跟真子老师一起舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.64,0:48:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:14.32,0:48:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:23.66,0:48:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再力一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.00,0:48:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.41,0:48:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:52.35,0:48:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边开始变的有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.56,0:48:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:19.45,0:49:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面也变热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:50.14,0:49:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚你是不是高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:55.08,0:49:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:56.95,0:49:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太舒服了就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.96,0:50:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师\N我想看你更多一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:05.36,0:50:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看真子老师\N多揉揉自己的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.37,0:50:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.57,0:50:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想看更多吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:26.45,0:50:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 尽情的看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.78,0:50:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以进一点看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:32.19,0:50:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:43.00,0:50:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸来看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:45.00,0:50:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:47.54,0:50:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.74,0:50:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.61,0:50:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:55.94,0:50:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师我已经忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:17.03,0:51:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的非常的舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.65,0:51:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以\N一直这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.46,0:51:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会再来一次高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:00.81,0:52:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.94,0:52:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用嘴你是没办法高潮的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.55,0:52:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们一起舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.29,0:52:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:13.75,0:52:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们要一起舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:48.46,0:52:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.88,0:53:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.26,0:54:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:23.08,0:54:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行喔 还不能射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:56.18,0:54:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么精神饱满呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.65,0:55:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒还是这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:21.81,0:55:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:28.35,0:55:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.22,0:55:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还是这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.83,0:55:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐\N怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.70,0:55:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.97,0:55:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不想要插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:47.57,0:55:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然很想\N可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.17,0:55:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:52.91,0:55:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.51,0:55:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:07.86,0:56:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想要看更多吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.73,0:56:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.19,0:56:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把真子老师看个遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:27.48,0:56:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揉揉看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:39.09,0:56:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.49,0:56:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫的肉棒要插进去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:47.23,0:56:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进去咯\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:06.58,0:57:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.05,0:57:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟真子老师合为一体了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:16.32,0:57:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:19.13,0:57:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:21.66,0:57:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.40,0:57:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你爽的一踏糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:43.68,0:57:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗\N等 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.02,0:57:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要爽死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:52.09,0:57:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.30,0:58:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么的硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.92,0:58:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.39,0:58:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想要更多 对吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.00,0:58:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会更舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.67,0:58:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好看着喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:42.54,0:58:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:47.75,0:58:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个姿势怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:50.95,0:58:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是不是看的很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.69,1:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.63,1:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 在忍耐一下不要射
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:50.40,1:00:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:53.47,1:00:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.28,1:01:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.81,1:01:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.48,1:01:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要插进来\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.49,1:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:07.89,1:01:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次来试试狗爬式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:10.29,1:01:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗爬式
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.96,1:01:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:14.96,1:01:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没试过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:18.97,1:01:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.57,1:01:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我可不可以插的进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.57,1:01:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:25.24,1:01:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:30.71,1:01:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:37.65,1:01:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.99,1:01:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N这个姿势也很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:53.27,1:01:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N你这不是插得很深吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:00.07,1:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 吞的好里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:04.48,1:02:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面被塞的满满的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.42,1:02:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.82,1:02:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看真子老师的大奶子\N可以哦 帮我脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.45,1:02:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样下去会坏掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.12,1:02:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的我好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.39,1:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.40,1:03:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄的人家很舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:15.62,1:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N好爽哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.49,1:03:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 还不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:23.89,1:03:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:44.18,1:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以射哦 知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.79,1:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想不想要继续舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:04.33,1:04:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的插 插到最里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:21.68,1:04:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.62,1:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整根都进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:30.89,1:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大肉棒在里面搅动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:34.23,1:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:56.12,1:04:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.66,1:05:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:12.80,1:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服 你还不能射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:17.34,1:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快点用力的干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:28.68,1:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:32.82,1:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:47.50,1:05:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 怎么样\N舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.45,1:06:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 我的小穴\N是不是又紧又舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.68,1:06:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你插的 插的好里面\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:48.63,1:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗 硬邦邦的大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:01.31,1:07:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 拉着我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.85,1:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 啊 要去了\N不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:23.33,1:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 你干的我好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.80,1:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 有没有感觉到\N我的小穴夹的很紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.88,1:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 在插里面一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:57.10,1:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 现在还不可以射\N在忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:13.51,1:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.25,1:08:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你的肉棒还这么坚挺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:19.52,1:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到就忍不住想要舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.73,1:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的快忍住不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:35.67,1:08:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你想要我怎么做\N快点告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.94,1:08:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:46.35,1:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要在哪里射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.35,1:08:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要插进来吗\N我想要更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.62,1:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就 尽情的插进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:13.04,1:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师 我想射在嘴里\N你想射在嘴里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:18.91,1:09:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.65,1:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在我的嘴里面射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:26.25,1:09:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘴里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:37.52,1:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要射了\N要射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:17.70,1:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我帮你舔个干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.26,1:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚在不停的颤抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.73,1:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道 因为你射了很多\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.07,1:12:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（最后我也忍不住跟小司一起做爱了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.94,1:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（但是）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.55,1:12:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那时我发现了一件事）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:09.75,1:12:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（比起做爱我对于那种）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:13.22,1:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那种又年轻又坚硬的肉棒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.29,1:12:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（更能让我兴奋的事实）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:23.63,1:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（没错）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.63,1:12:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我对那种年轻又挺的肉棒情不自禁了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:37.24,1:12:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（所以我借由替田径队加油的名义）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.32,1:12:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我的行为逐步的失控了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:09.28,1:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有没有读进去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:11.01,1:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:12.21,1:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么书啊\N啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.08,1:13:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想说艺\N多学一点课外知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.89,1:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是习题嘛\N啊 好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.76,1:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得老子站在\N这里帮你们看功课
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.50,1:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会现在开始努力学习的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.36,1:13:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我认真点行不行\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:32.37,1:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可上不大学哦\N嗯 我知道了 我会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.31,1:13:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多看看你旁边的西村
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.71,1:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是那个啦\N不要乱说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:51.32,1:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了我会杀了你\N说一下会死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:55.46,1:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙\N到底怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.26,1:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（敲门声）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:07.87,1:14:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位辛苦了\N啊 小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.14,1:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用帮你们准备晚餐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:14.54,1:14:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他们家里好像有准备好了\N谢谢老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:17.21,1:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢老师\N嗯 请用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:23.88,1:14:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师我读完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:26.02,1:14:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:27.62,1:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N嗯 真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:32.83,1:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边不是还没写吗\N不不不 已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:34.83,1:14:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我认真一点啊\N我已经写完啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.23,1:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都给我偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.30,1:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 老师你之前说\N要给我看的照片比较重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:41.77,1:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N给我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:43.77,1:14:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N我也努力的看了书对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:47.24,1:14:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我们去吧\N可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:50.31,1:14:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那西村你读完了再叫我啊\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:53.91,1:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就树好学习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:59.79,1:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你说的照片在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.26,1:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.19,1:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个小子\N别想绍我搞什么花样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:11.40,1:15:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师我不会的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.67,1:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人在学习小声一点哦\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:17.54,1:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（老师当时真的很帅）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:21.27,1:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（老师这个是你吗）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:23.41,1:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（才不是 是这个）\N（啊 原来是这个）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:25.95,1:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（跟现在完全不一样啊）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:28.35,1:15:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（也不是那个 是这边这个）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:31.42,1:15:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（果然很帅）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:34.35,1:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我就说吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:47.30,1:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我也要加油一点了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:52.64,1:15:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（老师谢谢你）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.52,1:16:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:04.92,1:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情想请教师母
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.12,1:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:17.33,1:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从武田那边听来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:21.07,1:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说师母会帮我们解决一些烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:27.34,1:16:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从武田君那边\N听来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:30.81,1:16:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:37.08,1:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:45.76,1:16:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里的烦恼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.23,1:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们下次做可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:04.04,1:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:06.85,1:17:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还在旁边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:15.12,1:17:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:20.19,1:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没关系了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.13,1:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:35.14,1:17:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:37.28,1:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有烦恼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:40.21,1:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:42.22,1:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好朐帮你解决烦恼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:47.15,1:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:51.69,1:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.03,1:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.70,1:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:03.70,1:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:08.24,1:18:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:10.11,1:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你希望我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:17.18,1:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.59,1:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手帮我尻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.59,1:18:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者用嘴巴帮我舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.26,1:18:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:32.93,1:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:36.54,1:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不能出声音哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.27,1:18:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被他们听到的\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:37.93,1:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚有说想让我帮你用手\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:21.17,1:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.18,1:20:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:27.18,1:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:29.18,1:20:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点舔吧 我要受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:35.59,1:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:45.87,1:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整根 都被吞下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.90,1:21:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.17,1:21:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在帮你口交哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:26.17,1:21:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽爆了\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:28.98,1:21:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要一直看着哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:32.91,1:22:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常奇妙的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:35.44,1:22:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要换这边咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:38.51,1:22:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边就算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:41.45,1:22:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是想让我舔这里\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.48,1:23:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.81,1:23:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以发出声音哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:18.42,1:23:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.82,1:23:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微忍耐一下\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:58.06,1:24:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边我也会帮你舔干净的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.60,1:24:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:10.87,1:24:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N爽炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:46.91,1:24:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:50.11,1:24:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的烦恼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:51.98,1:24:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:54.91,1:24:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想请你用那个\N大奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:59.85,1:25:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的大奶子夹住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:03.59,1:25:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹住道个大肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.60,1:25:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就帮你完成愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:20.41,1:25:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样\N啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:31.88,1:25:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N非常舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.77,1:25:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整根都被我夹住了呢\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:03.25,1:26:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你更舒服一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:19.40,1:26:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 想不想揉揉我的太奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:23.54,1:26:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我很想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.34,1:26:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:55.57,1:26:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好幸福\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.72,1:27:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:11.58,1:27:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的 奶头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:18.12,1:27:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我也摸你的奶头吗\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.13,1:27:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也要哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:32.54,1:27:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.74,1:27:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你舔他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:40.95,1:27:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:50.69,1:27:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以发出声音哦\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:57.90,1:28:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由自主想叫出来\N稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:18.18,1:28:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也帮你舔\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:29.53,1:28:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:41.27,1:28:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 西村 还在吗\N啊 在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:43.81,1:28:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在学习吗\N有 有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:46.88,1:28:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我快一点哦\N啊...好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:50.75,1:28:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N被吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:52.75,1:28:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想咯\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:29.72,1:29:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.12,1:29:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.54,1:30:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.01,1:30:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.94,1:30:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要射在嘴里\N尽情的射在我的嘴里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.68,1:30:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:32.78,1:31:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 射了好多出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:54.53,1:31:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.60,1:31:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒 非常的舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.54,1:32:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:03.61,1:32:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:05.74,1:32:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 还有许多的同学\N也有许多的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.75,1:32:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望真子老师\N也可以帮助他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:17.76,1:32:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:21.09,1:32:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有烦恼\N的同学我都欢迎哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:26.16,1:32:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢你了\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:29.23,1:32:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:31.77,1:32:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对那个人保密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:38.31,1:32:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:48.19,1:32:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 进来吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:50.99,1:32:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我的欲望就这样日与俱增）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:56.19,1:32:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（假借解决他们的烦恼为由）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:58.73,1:33:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（实际上是也许多坚挺的年轻肉棒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:02.47,1:33:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（一起舒服的过着每一天）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:09.68,1:33:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师他应该不会突然回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:13.01,1:33:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我刚打电话确认过了\N他还在学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:18.08,1:33:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样\N不要太在意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:23.29,1:33:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有烦恼吗\N啊...有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.49,1:33:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里的烦恼吧\N嗯...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:36.23,1:33:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以碰他吗\N嗯 麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:52.12,1:33:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里会让你最舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:55.19,1:33:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 在这里附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:00.26,1:34:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:02.39,1:34:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就开动了\N嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:07.60,1:34:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把上衣脱掉吧\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:09.87,1:34:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我脱掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:49.37,1:34:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:53.11,1:34:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的这根肉棒很大呢\N的确是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:59.79,1:35:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:02.72,1:35:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服呢\N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:07.13,1:35:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 要是更舒服\N会变成什么样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.61,1:35:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样子\N你是没办法满足的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:31.02,1:35:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连内裤也脱下来吧\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:41.96,1:35:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:44.76,1:35:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到这么大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:51.30,1:35:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越可以舔他吗\N嗯 可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:55.97,1:35:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 非常的大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:01.85,1:36:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:22.67,1:36:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:27.47,1:36:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒真的很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:49.23,1:36:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也需要我舔吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:12.05,1:37:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N非常的爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:15.12,1:37:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:30.74,1:37:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也需要舔干净一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:38.88,1:37:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:44.08,1:37:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:01.57,1:38:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:03.84,1:38:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来摸我吧\N可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:08.11,1:38:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:11.71,1:38:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢怎么来就怎么来\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:53.75,1:38:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想揉揉你的大奶子\N可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:58.82,1:39:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:05.76,1:39:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你面没有穿吗\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:11.50,1:39:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奶头的位置都这么清楚\N快 用力点揉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:22.98,1:39:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:25.92,1:39:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想要伸进去揉揉\N嗯 我想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:32.72,1:39:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:38.73,1:39:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点摸嘛\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:44.60,1:39:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子如何\N太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:15.17,1:40:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:35.45,1:40:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你看更多一点\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:48.93,1:40:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看\N好 好漂亮的奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:52.80,1:40:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N非常的 非常的漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:55.47,1:40:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很想摸她\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:58.01,1:41:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就尽情的蹂躏她吧\N我会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:43.25,1:41:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:46.72,1:41:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有没有想看哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.86,1:41:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看这里\N你想快看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:57.40,1:41:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:58.87,1:42:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那给你看个有意思的\N嗯 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:07.55,1:42:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看是什么\N好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:11.28,1:42:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:13.82,1:42:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个让自己舒服\N那你就快点用给我看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:18.22,1:42:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.23,1:42:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那作为交换\N我可以尽情的帮你口交吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:24.76,1:42:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:33.04,1:42:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你的大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:25.49,1:43:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:31.63,1:43:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:33.63,1:43:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才有说想看我的小穴吧\N嗯 对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:41.11,1:43:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:44.04,1:43:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你要的小穴哦\N太美丽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:54.85,1:43:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:58.06,1:44:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何\N非常 非常的漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:02.33,1:44:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么淫荡的小穴第一次看到吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:08.73,1:44:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常 非常的漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:13.40,1:44:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N我只要这样做她就会变很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:26.08,1:44:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:33.83,1:44:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:40.50,1:44:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:42.77,1:44:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让我的小穴变得更舒服的\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:55.45,1:44:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了 要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:58.78,1:45:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看点看我的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:12.66,1:45:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:16.67,1:45:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴已经这么湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:22.01,1:45:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你想做什么\N我 我想舔她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:27.21,1:45:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:30.95,1:45:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一起互相舔吧\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:33.48,1:45:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:37.62,1:45:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就尽情的舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:41.23,1:45:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:23.00,1:47:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:23.00,1:48:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:33.00,1:49:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:37.00,1:49:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:40.00,1:49:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法回头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:47.00,1:49:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只想舔年轻的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:30.00,1:50:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的比赛真精彩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.00,1:50:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.00,1:50:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:50.00,1:50:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武田也那么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:55.00,1:50:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真感谢他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:59.00,1:51:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:03.00,1:51:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我照顾他们
